node.name: Common Ports and Protocols
node.rich_text:
Common Ports and Protocols 20/21 (TCP) FTP 22 (TCP) SSH 23 (TCP) Telnet 25 (TCP) SMTP 80 (TCP) HTTP 161 (TCP/UDP) SNMP 389 (TCP/UDP) LDAP 443 (TCP) SSL/TLS (HTTPS) 445 (TCP) SMB 3389 (TCP) RDP
3389 is the default port for Remote Desktop Services and is a good indicator the machine being scanned is running windows
